query:
SELECT c.id, c.username, c.firstName, c.lastName, 
       a.id as assignment_id, a.jobId, a.status, a.startDate, a.endDate,
       j.title as job_title
FROM contractors c
LEFT JOIN jobAssignments a ON c.id = a.contractorId
LEFT JOIN jobs j ON a.jobId = j.id
WHERE c.username = 'john';
